The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and deep learning, which are covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it specifically deals with NLP. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories as they cover deep learning. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category as it deals with neural networks, which are used in the paper. Finally, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper analyzes the mechanism of self-attention, which is used in computer vision tasks.
